## ğŸ›’ Trenzzo MERN Multi-Vendor E-Commerce Platform ##
A production-grade, multi-vendor e-commerce application built using the MERN stack, supporting Admin, Seller, and Shopper roles, real-time notifications, secure authentication, OTP verification, and online payments.
This project focuses on real-world architecture, not demo-level CRUD.

